1
00:00:24,360 --> 00:00:28,360
Peter and Benjamin were planning a harvest feast.

2
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:35,370
"We need berries," Peter said.

3
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:40,710
"Let's gather some nuts too," Benjamin said.

4
00:00:40,710 --> 00:00:44,380
"A harvest feast must have nuts!"

5
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:53,050
The bunnies gathered some berries.

6
00:01:01,060 --> 00:01:03,730
Then they looked for nuts.

7
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:13,740
Peter and Benjamin saw lots of squirrels.

8
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:18,410
The squirrels were gathering nuts for winter.

9
00:01:20,410 --> 00:01:22,750
It was hard work!

10
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:31,430
Peter and Benjamin put their nuts in a pile.

11
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:34,760
"We have a big pile now," Peter said.

12
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:38,100
"Hey!" shouted a squirrel.

13
00:01:38,100 --> 00:01:40,430
It was Timmy Tiptoes.

14
00:01:40,770 --> 00:01:43,770
Timmy ran toward the bunnies.

15
00:01:43,770 --> 00:01:46,110
He pointed at their big pile.

16
00:01:46,110 --> 00:01:50,440
"Are you stealing my nuts?" he asked.

17
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:53,450
Timmy looked at Benjamin and Peter.

18
00:01:54,450 --> 00:01:56,120
"No," Peter said.

19
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,790
"We collected these nuts."

20
00:02:00,450 --> 00:02:03,790
"Hmph!" Timmy was mad.

21
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:07,130
"I put my nuts right there."

22
00:02:07,130 --> 00:02:11,800
"Well, these are our nuts," Benjamin said.

23
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,470
Timmy frowned.

24
00:02:14,470 --> 00:02:17,470
"Then where are my nuts?"

25
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:21,480
Benjamin shrugged. "I don't know."

26
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:30,820
"But we will find out!" Peter said.

27
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:09,860
Peter and Benjamin looked for the missing nuts.

28
00:03:17,530 --> 00:03:20,870
Timmy gathered new ones.

29
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:32,550
"The squirrels are very busy," Peter said.

30
00:03:32,550 --> 00:03:35,220
"They are gathering lots of nuts."

31
00:03:35,550 --> 00:03:39,550
"Winter is coming," Benjamin said. "They need—"

32
00:03:39,550 --> 00:03:43,560
"Hey!" A squirrel suddenly shouted.

33
00:03:43,890 --> 00:03:47,560
"Look at my pile!" a second squirrel cried.

34
00:03:47,890 --> 00:03:52,230
"Who stole my nuts?" a third squirrel yelled.

35
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:56,900
More squirrels came running.

36
00:03:57,240 --> 00:04:00,240
One squirrel shouted at Timmy Tiptoes.

37
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:03,910
"Did you steal our nuts?" she cried.

38
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:06,580
"No!" Timmy said.

39
00:04:06,580 --> 00:04:09,580
"Someone took some of my nuts too."

40
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,900
"There is a nut thief!"

41
00:04:13,250 --> 00:04:16,590
The squirrels shouted back and forth.

42
00:04:20,590 --> 00:04:24,930
Just then Peter spotted a fat squirrel.

43
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:29,600
"Look, Benjamin!" Peter whispered.

44
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,940
"It's Silvertail."

45
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:35,940
Silvertail slipped over to the nut piles.

46
00:04:36,610 --> 00:04:38,950
The squirrels were still fighting.

47
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:42,620
They did not see Silvertail.

48
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:45,620
He took nuts from a pile!

49
00:05:06,310 --> 00:05:08,310
Silvertail hid the nuts under a log.

50
00:05:09,980 --> 00:05:13,650
Then he laughed.

51
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:20,320
"I have lots of nuts for winter. I don't have to work at all!"

52
00:05:47,010 --> 00:05:51,020
Peter looked at Benjamin.

53
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:55,000
"Silvertail is the nut thief!"

54
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:59,360
The bunnies ran to the squirrels.

55
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:03,700
"We found the nut thief!" Peter said.

56
00:06:04,700 --> 00:06:07,370
"Go away!" a squirrel said.

57
00:06:07,370 --> 00:06:11,040
"This is not bunny business," another yelled.

58
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:14,040
"It is squirrel business!"

59
00:06:14,370 --> 00:06:16,710
Timmy looked at the bunnies.

60
00:06:16,710 --> 00:06:20,050
"Who is the nut thief?" he asked.

61
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:23,380
"Come with us," Benjamin said.

62
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:27,050
"We will show you."

63
00:06:27,050 --> 00:06:29,720
Timmy followed the bunnies.

64
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:41,740
They showed him Silvertail's hiding spot.

65
00:06:43,740 --> 00:06:46,070
Timmy's eyes got big.

66
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:48,740
"Wow!" he said.

67
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:55,750
"Silvertail is stealing our nuts! We must stop him."

68
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:59,420
Benjamin saw a hollow tree.

69
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:01,760
It had a hole in its trunk.

70
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:08,760
"Hmm," Benjamin said. "I have an idea."

71
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:15,430
The bunnies got some nuts.

72
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:19,110
They hopped to the hollow tree.

73
00:07:20,770 --> 00:07:24,110
Then they pushed the nuts into the hole.

74
00:07:25,780 --> 00:07:31,120
"Now let's find Silvertail!" Benjamin said.

75
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:46,800
Silvertail was taking a nap.

76
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:55,140
"Hi, Silvertail!" Peter woke him up.

77
00:07:56,480 --> 00:08:00,810
"We found lots of nuts. Would you like some?"

78
00:08:01,820 --> 00:08:06,820
"Yes!" Silvertail licked his lips.

79
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:27,840
The bunnies brought Silvertail to the tree.

80
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:36,850
Silvertail looked in the hole.

81
00:08:36,850 --> 00:08:44,190
"I don't see any nuts. Where are—Yikes!"

82
00:08:44,190 --> 00:08:48,540
Silvertail fell into the hole.

83
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:53,300
"Ahh!" he cried. "I'm stuck!"

84
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:57,000
The bunnies laughed.

85
00:08:58,540 --> 00:09:02,210
"The nut thief is trapped!" Peter said.

86
00:09:02,210 --> 00:09:06,880
"Good-bye, Silvertail!" Benjamin said.

87
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:16,220
The bunnies told the squirrels about Silvertail.

88
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:19,230
The squirrels stopped fighting.

89
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:22,560
"I have a great idea," Timmy said.

90
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:25,230
"Let's share our nuts!"

91
00:09:31,570 --> 00:09:34,570
The squirrels shared all the nuts.

92
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:37,910
Timmy gave some to the bunnies.

93
00:09:39,250 --> 00:09:42,920
"Thank you for helping us," Timmy said.

94
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:47,590
"We can save these nuts for our feast!" Peter said.

95
00:09:51,930 --> 00:09:55,260
At last it was time for the harvest feast.

96
00:09:55,930 --> 00:09:58,930
All the squirrels came.

97
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,610
Timmy rubbed his belly.

98
00:10:05,610 --> 00:10:09,280
"These nut pies are delicious!"

99
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:12,280
Then someone else appeared.

100
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:15,620
Peter gasped. "Silvertail!"

101
00:10:15,620 --> 00:10:18,620
Benjamin laughed.

102
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:23,290
"He's not fat anymore!"

103
00:10:23,620 --> 00:10:25,960
Silvertail frowned at the bunnies.

104
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:31,630
"You trapped me in the tree! And where are all my nuts?"

105
00:10:32,300 --> 00:10:36,300
Peter pointed to the nut pies.

106
00:10:36,300 --> 00:10:41,310
Everyone—but Silvertail—laughed.

